{"tid":285861,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆叫我同男朋友分手，應該點做","createTime":"2017-06-16T07:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T12:35:51.000Z","uid":31374,"like":2,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"767f448889b4e1ccb86dc608f0b1103f4779e563","tid":285861,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:15:09.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左六年，拍到而家大家都year2<br />\n佢對我好好，咩都會就哂我<br />\n每晚都會facetime唱歌哄我訓<br />\n又唔會強迫我做自己唔想做既野(e.g.搞野)<br />\n佢話我個處應該等佢第時做我老公先破<br />\n我好多次都感動到想喊<br />\n不過我知佢唔想我喊所以忍住<br />\n <br />\n問題黎喇<br />\n佢讀緊乞食科<br />\n醫科出生既老豆話跟住佢下半生一定會好辛苦<br />\n叫我快d同佢分手，長痛不如短痛<br />\n雖然入大學以黎識得一年，但老豆真係好可靠<br />\n我地全組人都當佢親生老豆一樣<br />\n可能佢真係講得岩...."},{"pid":"d0a47ba582deb7b62b242ee3598b4d3fc39c1175","tid":285861,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"同老豆做愛"},{"pid":"c0e71b1884304cafc163a1fd371c254c7f85c15b","tid":285861,"uid":44412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:16:36.000Z","msg":"我地全組人都當佢親生老豆一樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ffdce6733ec43fd5caf346ec51242de01435ff","tid":285861,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:16:39.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f3a5bdaddcd432cc36b364f2259ca79cec62aa","tid":285861,"uid":47845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:16:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6d4e8dcbfb8e59ea3c677843ec110fdef5071ddd","tid":285861,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:18:01.000Z","msg":"0分重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2b0f2ce7b8ec4ca4e1101483ae29575695d7b6","tid":285861,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:18:41.000Z","msg":"哩個故事每日上演幾多次?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3